pixel hota hai hamesha fixed
percent hota hai parent pr dependent
vw screen ki width
vh viewport height.. screen ki height
vmax dono width or height ko dekh rha hota hai 
em... let say apke parent mn font size 10px hai ... ab yhi font agr child ka 2em hega toh means
yeh hojaega 20px bcz 10+10 = 20.... so yhe parent ko lekr chalta hai 
rem root em ... means yeh k root ko leta hai.. 1 rem = 16px (fixed  )
ch= kitne charcters ki width.
lh = line height!

flex-wrap: wrap and nowrap
flex-shrink: 0 phela wala div shrik nhi karega!! (yeh child ko doge)


